        title: '2. Changes to Terms',
        content: [
            `We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. We will provide notice of any material changes by posting the updated Terms on our platform and updating the "Last Updated" date. Your continued use of the Services after such changes constitutes your acceptance of the new Terms.`,
        ],
    },
