        id: 'account',
        title: '3. Account Registration',
        content: [
            'To access certain features of our Services, you may need to create an account. You agree to provide accurate, current, and complete information during the registration process and to update such information to keep it accurate, current, and complete.',
            'You are responsible for safeguarding your password and for all activities that occur under your account. You agree to notify us immediately of any unauthorized use of your account.',
        ],
    },
    {
        id: 'content',
        title: '4. User Content',
        content: [
            `Our Services allow you to post, link, store, share, and otherwise make available certain information, text, graphics, videos, or other material ("User Content"). You are responsible for the User Content that you post, including its legality, reliability, and appropriateness.`,
